<plot>Highlights of the New York Yankees' 1978 season, including footage from regular-season, playoff and World Series action, as well as some archival interviews. The Yankees trailed rival Boston by 14 games in mid-July but rallied to win the pennant, then won the LCC and World Series for their 22nd title.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?269849</url></doc>
